reviewText: Yea this is an ok movie with a great message. BEWARE WHO YOU TRUST AND WHO YOU HOOK UP.

This movie is probably the most original movie I've ever seen.  I know there're morre like it, but they're not quite the same. The only reason I didn't give it five stars was because of the way it was filmed.  Don't get me wrong, the filming is great,but the camera didn't seem right.
